Homepage: https://github.com/Kirlif/HBC-Tool
Description: Hermes Bytecode Disassembler and Assembler
 A command-line interface for disassembling and assembling the
 Hermes Bytecode. Provides tools for working with Hermes bytecode
 files used in React Native applications and JavaScript engines.
